@startuml
title EIP-1167 Clone Architecture (Factory + Partner Proxy)
left to right direction

actor Partner
actor Sender

rectangle "RateProxyFactory" as Factory
rectangle "ServiceDepositProxy\nImplementation" as Impl
rectangle "ServiceDepositProxy\nClone (Partner Instance)" as Clone
rectangle "RatingRouter" as Router
node "Chainlink DON" as Don
cloud "External API\npumpdumpapp.com" as Api

Partner --> Factory : deploy/use
Factory --> Impl : deploy once in constructor
Factory --> Clone : Clones.clone(Impl)
Factory --> Clone : initialize(router, owner=msg.sender)

Partner --> Clone : setPartnerUsers(...)
Sender --> Clone : depositFor(beneficiary)
Clone --> Router : requestRating(sender)
Router --> Don : _sendRequest(...)
Don --> Api : HTTP GET /api/rate/{sender}
Don --> Router : callback(rating)
Router --> Clone : handleRating(requestId, sender, rating)

note bottom of Clone
Accepted:\n balances[beneficiary] += amount
\nRejected:\n refund sender
end note

@enduml
